snippet.title: [CAVE] Mushihimesama BUG PANIC Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
FALL 2010 A New CAVE Adventure for iPhone and iPod touch!
Catch the Bug Panic Fever! 

Insect princess Reco of the infamous shooting game "Mushihimesama" and
"Mushihimesama Futari" is off on a new adventure!  Bring the insect kingdom back to order in "Mushihimesama BUG PANIC": CAVE's first adventure game for the iPhone and iPod touch! 


Mushihimesama Bug Panic!
